<lb n="0543a23" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0543013">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0543013">佛說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0543013"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頞多和多耆經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0543a24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0543a25" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">失譯<note resp="Taisho" n="0543014" place="foot text" type="orig">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【宮】，人＋（名）【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0543014" type="mod">人【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】，人名【明】</note><app n="0543014"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">人名</rdg></app>今附西晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0543a26" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT17p0543a2601">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT17p0543a2604" cb:place="inline">一時佛在為耶國時有多樹木處，與
<lb ed="T" n="0543a27"/>眾比丘僧俱，比丘有五百人。月十五日盛<note n="0543015" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">滿＝湯【宮】</note><note n="0543015" type="mod" resp="CBETA">滿【大】，湯【宮】</note><app n="0543015"><lem wit="【大】">滿</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">湯</rdg></app>
<lb n="0543a28" ed="T"/>時，夜半寂然安靜，比丘僧自相難問。時栴檀
<lb n="0543a29" ed="T"/>調弗天人，持天形狀威神光耀來，直前趣佛。
<pb ed="T" n="0543b" xml:id="T17.0740.0543b"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0543b01"/><note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0543016" resp="Taisho">前以後＝至佛前已【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0543016">至佛前已【CB】【磧-CB】【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，前以後【大】</note><app n="0543016"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【磧-CB】">至佛前已<note type="cf1">Q20_p0155a26</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">至佛前已</rdg><rdg wit="【大】">前以後</rdg></app>，悉脫身上珍寶著一面，但<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0543017" resp="Taisho">披＝被【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0543017" type="mod">披【大】，被【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543017"><lem wit="【大】">披</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">被</rdg></app>一領
<lb n="0543b02" ed="T"/>衣，前以頭面著佛足，禮畢問佛言：「諸可過去
<lb n="0543b03" ed="T"/>佛正覺弟子有經，<note resp="Taisho" n="0543018" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0543018" type="mod">經【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543018"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>名《頞多和多<note resp="Taisho" n="0543019" place="foot text" type="orig">耆＋（經）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0543019" type="mod">耆【大】，耆經【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543019"><lem wit="【大】">耆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">耆經</rdg></app>》，佛弟
<lb ed="T" n="0543b04"/>子今亦復說是頞多和多耆經。願佛為我說
<lb ed="T" n="0543b05"/>是經，當使弟子奉持。」佛默然不<note n="0543020" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">應＋（而）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0543020" resp="CBETA">應【大】，應而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543020"><lem wit="【大】">應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">應而</rdg></app>。栴檀調
<lb ed="T" n="0543b06"/>弗稽首而却坐。</p><p cb:place="inline" xml:id="pT17p0543b0607">佛即為比丘僧說經言：「我為
<lb n="0543b07" ed="T"/>若說《頞多和多耆經》，皆聽著心中，念之勿得
<lb ed="T" n="0543b08"/>忘。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0543b0802" cb:place="inline">比丘言：「願佛說，我皆當受經戒。」</p><p cb:place="inline" xml:id="pT17p0543b0814">佛言：「布
<lb n="0543b09" ed="T"/>施有八事。何謂為八？愚癡人布施但布施，不
<lb ed="T" n="0543b10"/>知其恩善所在。既布施不達世間無有常，癡
<lb n="0543b11" ed="T"/>人持作常。世間苦無極，愚人持作樂。世間所
<lb ed="T" n="0543b12"/>有，愚人言『是我所有，可常得』。世間人皆顛倒，
<lb ed="T" n="0543b13"/>不淨、臭處、惡露，愚人用作好；不知作善得善，
<lb ed="T" n="0543b14"/>作惡得惡，愚人施與人，不知其人德深淺，持
<lb ed="T" n="0543b15"/>善心施與得道者，<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0543021" resp="Taisho">（其）＋福【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0543021" type="mod">福【大】，其福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543021"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">其福</rdg></app>不可量。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0543b16"/><p xml:id="pT17p0543b1601">佛告諸比丘：「何以知愚人不知布施？有十因
<lb n="0543b17" ed="T"/>緣。何等為十？愚人布施<note n="0543022" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔不知〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543022" type="mod" resp="CBETA">不知【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543022"><lem wit="【大】">不知</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>為尊，自用<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0543023" resp="Taisho">所＝不【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0543023">所【大】，不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543023"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不</rdg></app>
<lb n="0543b18" ed="T"/>與者得善；愚人<note n="0543024" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">不＋（以）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0543024" resp="CBETA">不【大】，不以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543024"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不以</rdg></app>至心施與人也；愚人既施
<lb ed="T" n="0543b19"/>與人，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0543025">〔與〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0543025" type="mod">與【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543025"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時不敬重；不自手與，傳教人與，施
<lb n="0543b20" ed="T"/>人<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0543026">不＋（久）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">不【大】，不久【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543026"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不久</rdg></app>欲望其福；不即得其福者，自用<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0543027" resp="Taisho">忘＝亡【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0543027">忘【大】，亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543027"><lem wit="【大】">忘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亡</rdg></app>其
<lb ed="T" n="0543b21"/>福；愚人施與佛、辟支佛、阿羅漢，不能自知其
<lb n="0543b22" ed="T"/>福大；愚人施與，不信佛、辟支佛、阿羅漢、阿那
<lb ed="T" n="0543b23"/>含、斯陀含、須陀洹；皆用為棄<note resp="Taisho" n="0543028" type="orig" place="foot text">損＝捐【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0543028">損【大】，捐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543028"><lem wit="【大】">損</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">捐</rdg></app>，無有後生；
<lb n="0543b24" ed="T"/>愚人施與，<note n="0543029" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">欲但＝但欲【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0543029" resp="CBETA">欲但【大】，但欲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543029"><lem wit="【大】">欲但</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">但欲</rdg></app>得名字，欲使人稱譽。是為
<lb ed="T" n="0543b25"/>愚人布施。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0543b2505" cb:place="inline">佛說經已，栴檀調弗及諸比丘，皆
<lb ed="T" n="0543b26"/>歡喜，前為佛作禮。</p></cb:div>
